<html>
<head>
<title>Split / Merge Customer Accounts</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/transactions.css">
<script>

	var allSelected = false;
	var maxCheckBoxValues = %%%max_checkboxes%%%;

</script>
<script src="js/customer_centric_interface.js"></script>
</head>
<h1>Customer SSN Change - Split</h1>
This customer has more than one account with the same original SSN and any selected accounts will be split<br>
into a new customer account.  Please verify the account(s) you wish to split from the original customer <br>
and merge into the new customer.<br>
<br>
The original account that the change was requested on:<br>
<table>
<tr>
<th>Application ID</th>
<th>Old Social Security Number</th>
<th>New Social Security Number</th>
<th>Customer Name</th>
<th>Employer</th>
</tr>
<td>%%%application_id%%%</td>
<td>%%%old_formatted_ssn%%%</td>
<td>%%%new_formatted_ssn%%%</td>
<td>%%%customer_name%%%</td>
<td>%%%employer_name%%%</td>
</table>
<br>
<form id="customer_ssn_change" method="post" action="/" class="no_padding">
<input type="hidden" name="action" value="customer_ssn_change">
<input type="hidden" name="old_customer_id" value="%%%old_customer_id%%%">
<input type="hidden" name="new_ssn" value="%%%new_ssn%%%">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="900">
<tr><td align="left" valign="top">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" class="%%%mode_class%%%">
  <tr class="height"><th colspan="0" style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;The following Application(s) are associated with the same customer.<br> Select the accounts you wish to split from the current customer and merge into the new customer.</th></tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="application_list_rows_table">
    <thead class="fixedHeader">
     <tr style="padding-top: 2px; border-bottom: 1px solid gray;">
       <th style="width: 40px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">Select</th>
       <th style="width: 100px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">Application ID</th>
       <th style="width: 100px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">SSN</th>
       <th style="width: 160px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">Name</th>
       <th style="width: 160px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">Email Address</th>
       <th style="width: 160px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid gray;">Employer</th>
       <th style="width: 180px; text-align: center;">Status</th>
     </tr>
     </thead>
     <tbody class="scrollContent" style="overflow: auto; height: auto;">
     %%%old_application_list%%%
     <tr>
     	<td colspan="6" align="left" style="text-align: left;"><!-- <input type="button" value="Select All / UnSelect All" onclick="javascript:SelectAllCheckBoxes('app')"> --></td>
     </tr>
     </tbody>
    </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
  <tr>
	<td colspan="6" align="left" style="text-align: left;">
		<input type="button" value="Split Customer" onclick="javascript:ConfirmSplit();">&nbsp;&nbsp;
		<input type="button" value="Cancel" onclick="javascript:window.close();">
	</td>
  </tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</form>